Package: luci-app-parental-privacy-vlan
Version: 1.3.0
Depends: luci-base, nftables, rpcd, rpcd-mod-rpcsys, udp-broadcast-relay-redux, umdns
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Edward Watts <edd@eddtech.co.uk>
Description: LuCI wizard and dashboard for a fully isolated Kids Network.
 Supports VLAN mode (DSA/OpenWrt 22.03+, mac80211 drivers: ath9k/ath10k/ath11k/mt76)
 and Bridge mode (Broadcom brcmfmac and other hardware lacking mac80211 VLAN support).
 Automatically detects hardware capability and selects the appropriate isolation method.
